FITPLAN.AI - PROJECT DOCUMENTATION
AI-Powered Fitness & Diet Planning Platform
February 2026

================================================================================
SECTION 1: PROBLEM STATEMENT
================================================================================

1.1 BACKGROUND
In the modern era, fitness and diet planning are crucial but people struggle with:
- Creating personalized fitness routines
- Following customized meal plans  
- Getting expert guidance without expensive personal trainers
- Tracking progress effectively

1.2 THE PROBLEM

PERSONALIZATION ISSUES:
• Generic workout plans that don't consider individual health conditions
• Meal plans ignore location-based food availability
• No consideration for food preferences (vegetarian/non-vegetarian)
• One-size-fits-all approach that doesn't work for diverse users

POOR USER ONBOARDING:
• Complex, multi-page forms users don't complete
• Unclear expectations about what data is needed
• No guidance on fitness level or health conditions
• Time-consuming setup process

LACK OF AI INTEGRATION:
• Static plans that don't adapt to user changes
• No intelligent recommendations based on health data
• Limited ability to generate varied meal plans
• Manual plan creation with human limitations

ACCESSIBILITY PROBLEMS:
• Not mobile-friendly  
• Difficult to navigate
• No quick reference for daily plans
• Poor data visualization

IMPACT:
Users waste time searching for generic fitness advice when they need:
✓ Personalized workout routines
✓ Region-specific meal plans
✓ Health condition awareness
✓ Easy-to-follow guidance
✓ Quantifiable progress tracking


================================================================================
SECTION 2: SOLUTION OVERVIEW
================================================================================

2.1 FITPLAN.AI SOLUTION

INTELLIGENT PERSONALIZATION:
• Uses Google Gemini AI for plan generation
• Considers location for regional cuisine
• Respects food preferences (veg/non-veg)
• Adapts to health conditions and fitness levels
• Real-time BMI calculation with target weight

STREAMLINED ONBOARDING (5-STEP):
Step 1: Basic Information (Name, Email, Age, Gender)
Step 2: Fitness Profile (Height, Weight, Level, Goal, BMI)
Step 3: Health & Preferences (Location, Health Issues, Food Pref)
Step 4: Confirmation (Review all details)
Step 5: Generation (AI creates personalized plans)

AI-POWERED PLAN GENERATION:
• Workout Plans: Customized exercises based on fitness level and goal
• Diet Plans: Location-aware, region-specific meals
• Real-time adaptation: Change preferences → Regenerate plans
• Specific quantities: Meals include exact ingredient amounts (not "1 plate")

USER-FRIENDLY DASHBOARD:
• Home View: Quick daily overview  
• Detailed Views: Complete meal and workout plans
• Progress Tracking: Visual charts and metrics
• Settings: Easy profile management
• Editable Food Preferences: Change anytime

2.2 KEY ADVANTAGES

PERSONALIZATION:
- AI learns from user data
- Location-aware meal suggestions (India/USA/Mediterranean specific dishes)
- Health-condition-aware workouts
- Food preference respect (vegetarian or mixed)

EFFICIENCY:
- Quick 5-step onboarding (5 minutes)
- Instant plan generation (3-5 seconds)
- No manual data entry after setup
- Easy profile updates in settings

ACCURACY:
- Real-time BMI calculation
- Specific meal quantities (Idli: 3 pieces, not "breakfast")
- Macronutrient tracking
- Evidence-based exercise recommendations

USABILITY:
- Simple, clean interface
- Mobile-responsive design
- Dark/light mode support
- Intuitive navigation


================================================================================
SECTION 3: TECHNOLOGY STACK
================================================================================

3.1 FRONTEND TECHNOLOGY

Framework:
• React 18 - Modern UI framework with hooks
• TypeScript - Type-safe development
• Vite - Lightning-fast build tool

Styling & UI:
• Tailwind CSS - Utility-first CSS framework
• Shadcn/UI - 40+ pre-built components
• Lucide React - Beautiful icons
• Responsive Design - Mobile-first approach

State Management:
• Zustand - Lightweight state management
• localStorage - Client-side data persistence

3.2 BACKEND TECHNOLOGY

Framework:
• FastAPI - High-performance Python web framework
• Python 3.10+ - Latest Python features

Database:
• MongoDB - NoSQL document database
• Collections: Users, Profiles, Plans
• Indexes: Email, User ID for fast queries

Authentication & Security:
• JWT (JSON Web Tokens) - 24-hour expiration
• bcrypt - Password hashing
• CORS - Cross-origin resource sharing
• Input Validation - Pydantic models

AI Integration:
• Google Gemini 2.5 Flash - Plan generation
• Prompt Engineering - Location & preference-aware
• Response Parsing - Structured JSON output

3.3 ARCHITECTURE

┌─────────────────────┐
│   User Browser      │
