SECTION 5: COMPLETE SYSTEM WORKFLOW
================================================================================

5.1 USER REGISTRATION & LOGIN

START
│
├─ User visits app
│  ├─ Check if authenticated (JWT in localStorage)?
│  │
│  YES → Dashboard
│  NO → Login/Register
│
├─ Registration Page:
│  • Email input
│  • Password input  
│  • Name input
│  • [Sign Up]
│
├─ Frontend validation
│  └─ Email format, password strength, name length
│
├─ POST /auth/register (Backend)
│  ├─ Check if email exists
│  ├─ Hash password (bcrypt)
│  ├─ Create user in MongoDB
│  ├─ Generate JWT (24h)
│  └─ Return token
│
├─ Frontend receives token
│  ├─ Store in localStorage
│  ├─ Update Zustand
│  └─ Redirect to Onboarding
│
└─ ONBOARDING


5.2 ONBOARDING WORKFLOW

STEP 1 → STEP 2 → STEP 3 → STEP 4 → STEP 5 → DASHBOARD

Step 1: Basic Info
Form: Name, Email, Age, Gender
Next: Go to Step 2

Step 2: Fitness Profile
Form: Height, Weight, Level, Goal
Calculate: BMI real-time
Target: Suggest target weight
Next: Go to Step 3

Step 3: Health & Preferences
Form: Location, Health Issues, Food Preference
Back: To Step 2
Next: To Step 4

Step 4: Confirmation
Display: All information
Edit: Click to go back to step
Confirm: Proceed to Step 5

Step 5: Generation (AI Plans)
Loading: Show spinner
Calls:
  - POST /ai/workout
  - POST /ai/diet
Success: Cache in store
Navigate: To Dashboard


5.3 PLAN GENERATION WORKFLOW

User Profile + Data
    ↓
Format Gemini Prompt
├─ User profile info
├─ Location (for meals)
├─ Food preference (veg/mixed)
├─ Health conditions
└─ Goal
    ↓
Call Gemini API
├─ genai.GenerativeModel("gemini-2.5-flash")
├─ Send prompt
└─ Receive response
    ↓
Parse Response
├─ Validate JSON
├─ Extract exercises/meals
└─ Check quantities
    ↓
Store in MongoDB
├─ Save workout_plans
└─ Save diet_plans
    ↓
Cache in Frontend
├─ Zustand store
└─ localStorage
    ↓
Display on Dashboard


5.4 FOOD PREFERENCE CHANGE WORKFLOW

Current: 'mixed'
User Action: Change to 'veg' in Settings

Onboarding: Drop down
- Mixed (Veg + Non-Veg)  
- Vegetarian Only

Select "Vegetarian Only"
    ↓
Click Save
    ↓
API: PUT /user/profile
{
  food_preference: 'veg',
  ...other fields
}
    ↓
Backend: Update database
    ↓
Frontend: Update Zustand
    ↓
Ask: "Regenerate plans?"
    ├─ YES:
    │  ├─ Clear old diet plans
    │  ├─ Call POST /ai/diet
    │  ├─ New plans (all vegetarian)
    │  └─ Display on page
    │
    └─ NO:
       └─ Keep existing plans


5.5 ERROR HANDLING

API Error
    ↓
Check Status:
├─ 401 Unauthorized:
│  ├─ Try refresh token
│  └─ If fails: redirect to login
│
├─ 400 Bad Request:
│  └─ Show validation message
│
├─ 500 Server Error:
│  └─ Show "Please try again later"
│
└─ Network Error:
   └─ Show "Check internet"
    ↓
Display Toast Notification
    ↓
User can retry


================================================================================
SECTION 6: DATABASE SCHEMA
================================================================================

USERS Collection:
{
  _id: ObjectId,
  email: String (unique),
  password_hash: String,
  name: String,
  created_at: DateTime,
  updated_at: DateTime
}

USER_PROFILES Collection:
{
  _id: ObjectId,
  user_id: ObjectId (foreign key, indexed),
  age: Number,
  gender: String,
  height: Number (cm),
  weight: Number (kg),
  fitness_level: String,
  goal: String,
  location: String,
  health_issues: Array,
  food_preference: String ('veg' or 'mixed'),
  updated_at: DateTime
}

WORKOUT_PLANS Collection:
{
  _id: ObjectId,
  user_id: ObjectId (indexed),
  days: Number,
  exercises: Array [
    {
      day: Number,
      name: String,
      exercises: Array
    }
  ],
  created_at: DateTime
}

DIET_PLANS Collection:
{
  _id: ObjectId,
  user_id: ObjectId (indexed),
  days: Number,
  meals: Array [...],
  location: String,
  food_preference: String,
  total_calories: Number,
  total_protein: Number,
  created_at: DateTime
}

Indexes:
- users.email (unique)
- user_profiles.user_id
- workout_plans.user_id
- diet_plans.user_id


================================================================================
SECTION 7: API ENDPOINTS SUMMARY
================================================================================

AUTHENTICATION:
POST /auth/register - Register user
POST /auth/login - Login user
POST /auth/refresh - Refresh token

USER PROFILE:
GET /user/profile - Get profile
PUT /user/profile - Update profile

AI PLANS:
POST /ai/workout - Generate workout
POST /ai/diet - Generate diet

PLANS MANAGEMENT:
GET /user/plans - Get all plans
GET /user/plans/workout/:id - Get workout
GET /user/plans/diet/:id - Get diet
POST /user/plans/clear - Clear all plans


